Javascript Bitcoin Exchange Rate Door for 
Synchronet BBS and ANSI capable terminals.
Graph of rates adapts to terminal size.
Data is pulled from Coinbase.com and no 
API Key is needed. Sysop configures their
local currency in /ctrl/modopts.ini file.
Orig Concept: BCR Coins @ BitSunrise.com.
